SUMMARY:
<summary>
This webpage presents the performance forecasts for Wanhua Chemical (stock code 600309) for several recent fiscal years. The most recent forecast for the fiscal year ending December 31, 2024, indicates an expected net profit attributable to shareholders of 1,303,306.66 million yuan, representing a year-on-year decrease of 22.49%. The company attributes this decline to factors including flat gross profit despite sales volume growth due to market price and raw material cost fluctuations, increased R&D and operating expenses, and asset impairment provisions. In contrast, the forecast for 2023 showed a modest increase of 3.57%. The 2022 forecast indicated a significant decrease of 34.12%, attributed to rising global energy and raw material costs outpacing revenue growth. The 2021 forecast showed a substantial increase of 145.47%, driven by new production capacity, increased supply capabilities, and favorable market conditions with rising chemical product prices. The page also includes a brief forecast for the first half of 2021, indicating a 380% increase.
</summary>

